---
/* Hero Section — Full viewport landing */
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center bg-glacial-bg overflow-hidden pt-24 pb-16 lg:pt-0 lg:pb-0">
  <!-- Decorative blur blobs -->
  <div
    class="absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-cyan/10 blur-[120px] animate-float pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>
  <div
    class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-indigo/10 blur-[100px] animate-float pointer-events-none"
    style="animation-delay: -3s;"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="container-main relative z-10 w-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8 items-center">

      <!-- Left: Content (7 cols) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">

        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="badge">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo animate-pulse"></span>
            Cohorte 1 — Places limit&eacute;es
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1
          class="mt-10 font-display font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.85] text-clinical-dark uppercase text-[length:var(--font-size-display)] reveal delay-1"
        >
          DEVIENS UN<br />
          FREELANCE<br />
          <span class="text-gradient">AUGMENT&Eacute;.</span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p
          class="mt-10 text-xl lg:text-2xl text-on-surface-muted font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xl border-l border-glacial-surface pl-8 reveal delay-2"
        >
          En 3 mois, ma&icirc;trise l'IA et l'automation pour structurer ton offre freelance et d&eacute;crocher tes premi&egrave;res missions.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA row -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 mt-12 reveal delay-3">
          <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-gradient btn-lg">
            R&eacute;server mon appel <span>&rarr;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#programme" class="btn btn-ghost">
            Voir le programme
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Social proof strip -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 mt-12 reveal delay-4">
          <div>
            <span class="block text-3xl font-black text-clinical-dark leading-none">500+</span>
            <span class="block text-sm text-on-surface-muted mt-1">automatisations d&eacute;ploy&eacute;es</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px bg-glacial-surface self-stretch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div>
            <span class="block text-3xl font-black text-clinical-dark leading-none">Make Partner</span>
            <span class="block text-sm text-on-surface-muted mt-1">1er Fran&ccedil;ais certifi&eacute; niveau 5</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Decorative visual (5 cols, hidden mobile) -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-5 reveal-right delay-3">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Main placeholder with deconstructed border -->
          <div class="deconstructed-border aspect-[4/5] bg-glacial-surface relative overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Subtle gradient overlay -->
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan/5 via-transparent to-indigo/5"
              aria-hidden="true"
            ></div>
            <!-- Grid pattern inside -->
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0"
              style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,240,255,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(79,70,229,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"
              aria-hidden="true"
            ></div>
            <!-- Diagonal line accent -->
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0"
              style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 40%, rgba(0,240,255,0.08) 50%, transparent 60%);"
              aria-hidden="true"
            ></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating badge -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-clinical-dark text-white p-6 border-l-4 border-cyan shadow-lg reveal-scale delay-5">
            <span class="eyebrow text-cyan/70 block mb-2">Status</span>
            <span class="font-display font-black text-lg tracking-tight uppercase">Syst&egrave;me augment&eacute;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
